Is the Nine Arch Bridge in Sri Lanka really worth it? 🤔🇱🇰

Everyone on Instagram hypes it up—but honestly, it’s just a short bridge with crowds and barely anything to do. The experience felt super overrated. 😒

Oh, and guess what? A plain omelette at a nearby café was ₹256! For real. 😂

Save your time (and your wallet)—there are way better places to explore in Ella.

#srilanka🇱🇰 #srilankatravel #ella #ninearchbridge #travelguide #traveltips

📍Must Visit This Holy Temple in Sri Lanka! 🇱🇰 

This is Ashoka Vatika 🙏🏻— the sacred garden where Sita Devi was kept captive by Ravana, according to the Ramayana. It is believed that Lord Hanuman first met Sita here, making it one of the most spiritually significant places for Hindu devotees.

🛕 Location: Seetha Amman Temple, Nuwara Eliya, Sri Lanka

🙏 A place where myth, history, and nature meet in divine harmony.

#ashokavatika #srilanka🇱🇰 #srilankatravel #hindu #hinduism #jaibajrangbali #jaishreeram #nuwaraeliya #seethaammantemple #ramayana
